data.description: Now available in Greystone! This 4 Bedroom, 3 Bathroom home also has an office, sits on a large quarter acre lot AND has a 4 CAR GARAGE! AND it COMES WITH SOLAR PANELS for great energy cost savings! The home has all you would expect to find in today's new construction. It's been extremely well maintained, has an open floorplan, split bedrooms, high ceilings, beautiful kitchen, tons of cabinet space, a large screened in back patio, and the backyard has room for a pool! Schedule your showing today!
